data.description: Don't overlook this rarely available property located in Elwood on an oversized lot with a pole barn! Situated on an expansive 0.75-acre plot and loaded with charm and character, this property provides an impeccable blend of indoor and outdoor living. With the numerous upgrades completed in the home itself, along with the fully finished pole barn, this residence is certain to surpass your expectations. Upon entering the main level, you'll be welcomed by an upgraded kitchen featuring granite countertops, modern appliances, and hardwood floors throughout. Stay cozy during the colder months in the spacious living room, complemented by a wood-burning stove. The main-level full bathroom showcases a Jacuzzi tub and a separate walk-in shower. The upper level boasts three generously sized bedrooms with ample closet and storage space. The private backyard is ideal for summer gatherings, offering plenty of room for furniture and seating on the new deck and additional concrete patio. The fully furnished 23x44 pole barn is a handyman's dream, fully equipped with gas and electric. And let's not forget the detached two-car garage! Noteworthy recent upgrades include a brand new roof installed in 2023, a new water heater, a new sump pump, new appliances, & new barn door. This residence is perfectly situated for commuters, with convenient access to the highway as well. Schedule your private tour today and don't miss the opportunity to own this one of a kind home yours today!
